review_title: Overall, the facilities were very good--clean, comfortable room and common areas.
good_review: The rooms were very clean which is probably the most important aspect for me when traveling. The housekeeping staff was very friendly and accommodating. I also liked the wonderful couch in the room with the two ottomans. It was so refreshing to have a comfortable place to watch TV and work on the computer. It also had the right amount of facilities in the lobby--a pleasant bar, sufficient tables to get together to talk, a business/work area, and a small snack/grocery store.
bad_review:
The breakfast was awful. The bagels tasted like paper, and there weren't really other options for a bread. A few muffins, different types of bread, maybe some Danish or croissants would have helped. We didn't bother after the first day; it was that bad. It could have been open a bit later as well.
Another problem--no available coffee after breakfast. Just having the coffee and real cream available all day makes a huge difference!
Paying for parking is the one thing that would deter us from coming back.

acommodation: King Studio Suite with Accessible Tub - Disability Access
good_review:
I liked that the property was close to my venue and it had a balcony to allow air to circulate. 
The staff is fantastic. See below!
bad_review:
I did not like the lack of attention to the elevator. It was down for two days, which allowed for only one elevator. This hotel is very busy, and having one elevator was inconvenient. But, I can live with that. 
What really sent me to a boil is a guest below decided to disregard the one courteous rule of pretty much EVERY hotel in the world—smoking!! The signs are all over the place, even marked on the slider towards the balcony and, yes, even ON the balcony! So, the disgusting plume of smoke wafted in my room above him. 
But, this is the redeeming part: I called the front desk, they promptly—I mean promptly— called the room and told the tenants that smoking is prohibited in the rooms and that there are designated smoking areas outside the hotel. Furthermore, they called me back and said if they continued, they would be told to leave! 
No more smoke for the remainder of my stay and I got to enjoy the fresh air from the balcony. 
Now, that’s service!!!

acommodation: Suite Estudio con cocina y sofá cama - Cama extragrande
good_review:
조식 포함이어서 좋았습니다. 조식이 다양하진 않지만 괜찮았습니다. 가족들 모두 아침식사를 즐길 수 있었습니다.
방은 깨끗했고 주차공간도 여유롭습니다.
bad_review: 방이 조금 습했습니다.

acommodation: Suite Estudio con cocina y sofá cama - Cama extragrande
good_review:
깔끔하고 편안한 객실
레지던스형 호텔이지만, 매일 침구정리 등간단한 서비스을 해줌
주변 비슷한 호텔대비 저렴한 가격
bad_review:
데스크 직원이 물품 결제를 잘못하여 불편하였음
주방 아일랜드 식탁 높이가 높아 앉기 불편
셀프세탁기, 건조기 사용시 1회용 세제를 번번히 구매해야함

acommodation: Suite Estudio con cocina y sofá cama - Cama extragrande
bad_review: 沙发床床垫特别不舒服。有洗衣房就更好了！

acommodation: Den Room with King Bed
review_title: Цена и качество не совсем отвечает стандарту! Завтраки включены, но нету никакого разнообразия, каждое утро одно и тоже!
good_review:
Близко к аэропорту, у меня было очень тихий номер звукоизоляции отличная, учитывая что аэропорт в 10 минутах езды на машине! 
￼
bad_review: Уборка номера была среднего качества, душевая кабина частично было с плесенью между плиткой! Один раз полотенца забыли поменять, и сложили красиво на полочку все использованные . ￼

acommodation: Habitación Doble - 2 camas dobles y sofá cama
review_title: 完全满足了我们此次入住的要求
good_review: 非常的方便，可以自由选择在大厅里休息、就餐，或者在房间里自己动手做料理，房间内还有洗碗机真的太好了，打扫房间也很自仔细。停车也很方便。
bad_review: 如果能在房间添加一点装饰摆件就更完美了
